# File Locations Quick Reference

| What | Where |
|------|-------|
| API startup, DI, middleware | `backend/TCG.Server/Program.cs` |
| REST controllers | `backend/TCG.Server/Controllers/` |
| SignalR hubs | `backend/TCG.Server/Hubs/` |
| Models, DTOs, interfaces | `backend/TCG.Core/` |
| Game turn logic, validation | `backend/TCG.GameLogic/` |
| EF migrations | `backend/TCG.Server/Migrations/` |
| Card definitions seed | `backend/TCG.Core/` or `TCG.Server/Data/` |
| Unit tests | `backend/TCG.Tests/` |
